title: Installation issue: tau@2.24.1 %gcc@8.2.0
body:
### Steps to reproduce the issue

I am trying to build TAU 2.24.1 but am coming up with an error.  It seems like Spack is trying to pass the -elf option to the TAU configure file (in the stage directory).  In other words, the offending command is this:

```console
./configure ... 
'-elf=/n/home09/ryantosca/spack/opt/spack/linux-centos7-x86_64/gcc-8.2.0/libelf-0.8.13-hi2dy6yq6fbjrczfmijelxybgvocjnyw'
```
But the configure script does not list elf as one of the valid options, so this is choking the build.

Also note: this appears to be an issue with tau@2.25, tau@2.26, tau@2.27.
